India Approves Payment Mechanism for Solar Grid-Connected Power

-- B y   A b h i j i t   R o y   C h o w d h u r y
-- 
2011-06-02T07:36:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-02/india-approves-payment-mechanism-for-solar-grid-connected-power.html
The Indian Cabinet approved a payment
mechanism for grid-connected solar power plants, according to a
statement today.  The government will spend 4.86 billion rupees to protect
solar projects against defaults by state-owned utilities, the
statement said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Abhijit Roy Chowdhury in New Delhi at 
 achowdhury11@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
